				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the land in North America.  For other uses, see <a href="Acadia_(disambiguation)" title="Acadia (disambiguation)">Acadia (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
